  }, "v17"), mdx("p", null, "T\xF4i khi\u1EC3n tr\xE1ch nh\u1EEFng ng\u01B0\u1EDDi c\xF3 uy t\xEDn trong Giu-\u0111a. T\xF4i h\u1ECFi, \"Chuy\u1EC7n \xE1c m\u1EA5y anh \u0111ang l\xE0m \u0111\xE2y ngh\u0129a l\xE0 g\xEC? M\u1EA5y anh xem ng\xE0y Sa-b\xE1t c\u0169ng nh\u01B0 c\xE1c ng\xE0y kh\xE1c. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v18"
  }, "v18"), mdx("p", null, "\u0110\xF3 ch\xEDnh l\xE0 \u0111i\u1EC1u t\u1ED5 ti\xEAn c\xE1c anh \u0111\xE3 l\xE0m cho n\xEAn Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF tr\u1EEBng ph\u1EA1t ch\xFAng ta v\xE0 th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 n\u1EA7y. B\xE2y gi\u1EDD m\u1EA5y anh l\u1EA1i khi\u1EBFn Ng\xE0i n\u1ED5i gi\u1EADn v\u1EDBi d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en th\xEAm b\u1EB1ng c\xE1ch l\xE0m nh\u01A1 nh\u1EDBp ng\xE0y Sa-b\xE1t.\" "), mdx("h6", {
